No, I am not a Busy Beaver.

5
00:01:37,380 --> 00:01:39,680
"绳子"

6
00:01:39,760 --> 00:01:41,810
您是常客吗？
Are you a Frequent Beaver?

7
00:01:41,890 --> 00:01:43,720
加入会员即可享用折扣
Join our rewards club for savings.

8
00:01:43,810 --> 00:01:46,640
购买本店提供的优惠商品
You can get your teeth into our dam good deals.

9
00:01:53,360 --> 00:01:54,400
别忘了
Don't forget:

10
00:01:54,480 --> 00:01:57,110
需要协助请向店员咨询
If you need help, ask a Beaver.

11
00:01:58,200 --> 00:01:59,740
哦
Oh.

12
