我能为你效劳吗？
Hey. Oh. Can I, uh, help you with that, sir?

13
00:02:03,200 --> 00:02:05,410
你觉得我不会割绳子？
Do you think I don't know how to cut rope?

14
00:02:06,210 --> 00:02:08,620
没啦，只是通常都由店员服务
No, it's just we usually do that for ya.

15
00:02:08,710 --> 00:02:12,840
你觉得我会割伤自己，然后告你们？
Do you think I'm gonna cut myself and bleed all over your floor and sue you?

16
00:02:15,130 --> 00:02:16,130
不是
No.

17
00:02:16,220 --> 00:02:17,550
那我就不需要帮忙
Then I don't need your help.

18
00:02:19,300 --> 00:02:20,640
祝你今天愉快
Have an excellent day.

19
00:02:22,390 --> 00:02:23,930
我是忙碌的河狸
I'm a Busy Beaver.

20
00:02:24,680 --> 00:02:25,680
白痴
Idiot.

21
