No, I know, but I can't put it into the computer the way that you just said.

34
00:03:07,930 --> 00:03:11,060
哪种电脑不会简单的算术？
What the hell kind of computer can't do simple math?

35
00:03:11,810 --> 00:03:14,230
-我要找店长 -他在吃午餐
-Can I speak to your manager? -He's at lunch.

36
00:03:14,940 --> 00:03:18,110
吃午餐，这年头大家只在乎吃吃吃
Lunch. All anyone cares about these days is lunch.

37
00:03:18,190 --> 00:03:20,780
-现场有谁可以负责？ -副店长？
-Is there anyone else in charge? -You want the assistant manager?

38
00:03:20,860 --> 00:03:22,910
-好的，请他来 -好喔
-Yes, I'd like the assistant manager. -'Kay.

39
00:03:25,530 --> 00:03:26,910
嘿，泰勒？
Hey, Taylor?

40
00:03:27,740 --> 00:03:29,830
泰勒？请到收银台
Taylor? To the front register.

41
00:03:29,910 --> 00:03:31,000
如何？
What's up?

42
00:03:31,080 --> 00:03:32,080
嘿，泰勒
Hey, Taylor.

43
00:03:32,830 --> 00:03:35,630
这就是副店长？她几岁？
This is the assistant manager? How old is she?

44
00:03:35,710 --> 00:03:37,340
妳不是该去上体育课吗？
Shouldn't you be in gym class?

45
00:03:37,420 --> 00:03:38,460
抱歉，什么？
Sorry, what?

46
00:03:38,550 --> 00:03:39,800
拿去，我有零钱
Here. I got some change.

47
00:03:39,880 --> 00:03:42,510
我替你付多出来的钱
Let me cover that extra 33¢ for you.

48
00:03:42,590 --> 00:03:46,470
我不要你的钱，这跟钱无关
Sir, I do not want your 33¢. And this is not about 33¢.

49
00:03:46,560 --> 00:03:47,560
事实是 我只要5呎长的绳子
This is about the fact that I got 5 feet of rope because I want 5 feet of rope.

50
00:03:50,480 --> 00:03:54,100
不应该付6呎长绳子的钱
And I shouldn't have to pay for 6 feet of rope if I don't want 6 feet.

51
00:03:54,190 --> 00:03:56,440
你要多拿1呎长的绳子吗？
Did you want another foot of rope?

52
00:05:05,760 --> 00:05:07,640
又来了
Not again.

53
00:05:27,660 --> 00:05:29,780
