嘿，你在干嘛？
Hey! What the hell?

57
00:06:00,650 --> 00:06:01,940
那是我的
That's mine.

58
00:06:02,020 --> 00:06:04,780
-应该停在单车架 -我只离开一下子
-It belongs in the bike rack. -I was only gone half a minute.

59
00:06:05,990 --> 00:06:09,240
下次我会把它锁进失物招领室
Next time, I'll lock it up in the lost and found.

60
00:06:10,530 --> 00:06:12,280
