"戴恩美利卡建设公司"

68
00:07:34,120 --> 00:07:37,240
再让那丑八怪尿在我门口看看
Don't you dare let that little rat dog piss on my walkway again.

69
00:07:37,330 --> 00:07:38,870
-我知道是妳 -别理他，王子
-I know it was you. -Ignore him, Prince.

70
00:07:38,950 --> 00:07:40,580
他是个超难搞老头子
He's a nasty, bitter old man. And he has no idea who's doing that.

71
00:07:40,660 --> 00:07:41,710
不知道是谁尿的

72
00:07:41,790 --> 00:07:43,790
妳家的绝对有尿
Well, it was one of you.

73
00:07:43,880 --> 00:07:48,710
叫妳那废柴男友别在大庭广众扭腰献宝
And tell that useless boyfriend of yours to stop stretching his groin in public.

74
00:07:50,630 --> 00:07:54,430
又不是14岁的体操选手
Looks like a 14-year-old Romanian gymnast, for God's sakes.

75
00:08:07,980 --> 00:08:09,990
快点，快滚开
Go on. Get outta here.

76
00:08:10,070 --> 00:08:11,070
快滚开
Go.

77
00:08:48,440 --> 00:08:49,440
"工程部门"

78
00:08:49,980 --> 00:08:51,940
大人物来了
There he is, the big man himself.

79
00:08:55,740 --> 00:08:57,200
这是在搞什么？
What's all this?

80
00:08:57,280 --> 00:08:59,790
退休蛋糕，庆祝你退休
It's, well, retirement cake, I guess. Call it what you like.

81
00:09:00,410 --> 00:09:01,620
"玩得开心"
"Have fun."

82
00:09:02,330 --> 00:09:03,660
玩得开心，
"Have fun."

83
00:09:03,750 --> 00:09:04,960
玩什么？
Doing what?

84
00:09:05,040 --> 00:09:08,380
下半辈子玩得开心啊，我们想…
Have fun with the rest of your life. We wanted to, you know...

85
00:09:09,090 --> 00:09:10,250
庆祝？
Celebrate?

86
00:09:10,340 --> 00:09:11,710
对啊，不，
Yes! Well, no.

87
00:09:11,800 --> 00:09:13,300
只是欢送你
Give you a nice send-off.

88
00:09:14,590 --> 00:09:15,800
欢送
"Nice."

89
00:09:15,880 --> 00:09:16,970
别这样，奥托
Come on, Otto.

90
00:09:17,050 --> 00:09:19,010
是你自己决定要走
You're the one who decided to leave.

91
00:09:19,100 --> 00:09:21,350
你也拿到不少资遣费
And you did get a nice severance package.

92
00:09:22,270 --> 00:09:24,350
你把我从营运部调走
You took me off Operations.

93
00:09:24,430 --> 00:09:26,230
削减我的工时
You cut back on my hours.

94
00:09:26,310 --> 00:09:29,730
把我训练的泰瑞升为我主管
You made Terry, who I trained, my supervisor.

95
00:09:29,820 --> 00:09:33,280
泰瑞没有手机就不知道何年何月
Terry, who can barely figure out what year it is without his phone.

96
00:09:33,360 --> 00:09:36,610
所以我是拿了资遣费
So, yes, I took the severance package.

97
00:09:36,700 --> 00:09:38,200
很遗憾你这么想
I'm sorry you see it that way.

98
00:09:38,280 --> 00:09:40,950
并购之后大家都得调适
We all had to adjust after the merger.

99
00:09:41,030 --> 00:09:44,870
但你这些年来对公司贡献良多
But you've been quite an asset to this company over the years, so--

100
00:09:44,960 --> 00:09:47,120
是真的，你非常可靠
You have. Reliable as hell.

101
00:09:47,210 --> 00:09:49,000
我们会怀念你订的进度表
We're gonna miss those schedules of yours.

102
00:09:50,960 --> 00:09:51,800
敬奥托！
To Otto!

103
00:09:51,880 --> 00:09:54,460
-敬奥托
-To Otto! -To Otto.

104
00:09:57,720 --> 00:10:00,890
奥托，要吃一块你的脸吗？
Okay, Otto. Want a piece of your face?

105
00:10:08,100 --> 00:10:09,100
谁饿了？
-Who's hungry?

106
00:10:09,860 --> 00:10:12,570
"此路不通 无证禁止停车"

107
00:10:12,650 --> 00:10:14,440
看看啊
Look at this.

108
00:10:14,530 --> 00:10:15,570
不行
No, no.

109
00:10:16,240 --> 00:10:17,650
嘿，等等
Hey, hey, wait!

110
00:10:17,740 --> 00:10:21,280
不不不，妳不可以没有许可就开进来
No, no, no. Hey, you cannot use this road without a permit.

111
00:10:21,370 --> 00:10:23,990
我没停车，只是运送包裹
I'm not parking. I just dropped off a package.

112
00:10:24,080 --> 00:10:26,870
招牌又没说可以运送包裹
The sign doesn't say anything about packages, does it?

113
00:10:26,960 --> 00:10:28,830
只说需要许可，妳没有许可
It says "permits" and you don't have one.

114
00:10:28,920 --> 00:10:30,880
这条街是条死巷
This is not a through street.

115
00:10:32,340 --> 00:10:33,800
祝您愉快，先生
Have a nice day, sir.

116
00:10:33,880 --> 00:10:35,260
妳每次开进来
Every time you come in here

117
00:10:35,340 --> 00:10:38,340
就代表有个住户不能停车
that means one of the residents can't park in front of their homes!

118
00:10:39,470 --> 00:10:42,430
别人不会这样，开白卡车的都很乖
The other guys don't do this. The guys with the white trucks.

119
00:10:42,510 --> 00:10:44,560
怎么你们棕色的都来乱？
How come it's always you brown guys?

120
00:10:44,640 --> 00:10:46,600
我说的不是妳的肤色
And I don't mean that racially!

121
00:10:54,530 --> 00:10:55,570
喂？
Hello.

122
00:10:55,650 --> 00:10:58,150
-抱歉，你听得到吗？
Oh, hi. Sorry, can you hear me?

123
00:10:58,240 --> 00:10:59,110
-是的
Yes.

124
00:10:59,200 --> 00:11:00,200
-我是苏珊
It's Susan.

125
00:11:00,280 --> 00:11:01,280
-哪位是苏珊？
Susan who?

126
00:11:01,370 --> 00:11:03,660
我有关于健保的好消息
I have great news about your health insurance.

127
00:11:03,740 --> 00:11:06,080
不不不，机器人！
Oh, no, no, no. Robot, robot, robot!

128
00:11:09,710 --> 00:11:13,630
我要找谁才能停用这支电话？
Well, who do I have to talk to to get this phone number disconnected?

129
00:11:13,710 --> 00:11:14,960
用户服务部门
That's Account Services.

130
00:11:15,050 --> 00:11:17,460
能帮我转接或是要按个号码？
Can you transfer me or should I press a number?

131
00:11:20,380 --> 00:11:23,640
我听那段音乐七分钟了
Well, I have been listening to that music for seven minutes.

132
00:11:23,720 --> 00:11:24,930
很抱歉，安德森先生
I do apologise, Mr Anderson.

133
00:11:25,010 --> 00:11:27,390
我想停止我家的供电
I would like the electricity shut off at this residence.

134
00:11:27,470 --> 00:11:30,270
-您要搬家？ -不，我要取消帐户
-Are you moving home? -No, I am cancelling the account.

135
00:11:30,940 --> 00:11:33,860
A-N-D-E-R-S-O-N.
A-N-D-E-R-S-O-N

136
00:11:33,940 --> 00:11:36,360
这六天为何不能退费？
And why can't you refund me for the six days?

137
00:11:36,440 --> 00:11:38,240
O-T-T-O.
O-T-T-O

138
00:11:38,320 --> 00:11:39,320
是公司规定
Oh, it's policy.

139
00:11:39,400 --> 00:11:42,780
我的规定是多付六天瓦斯费
Well, my policy is that if I'm going to pay for six days of gas,

140
00:11:42,870 --> 00:11:45,240
就能多用六天的瓦斯
then I will use six days of gas.

141
00:11:45,910 --> 00:11:46,990
就这样
Then we are done here.

142
00:11:49,830 --> 00:11:50,830
白痴
Idiots.

143
00:13:06,780 --> 00:13:07,780
好了
Okay.

144
00:13:09,120 --> 00:13:10,790
往前，停下来，往前
Go, go, go. Stop. Go.

145
00:13:11,620 --> 00:13:12,960
好了，停下来
Okay. Yeah. Stop.

146
00:13:15,250 --> 00:13:18,170
倒车，你看不到，小心点，用原力
Back. You're in the blind spot, be careful. Use the Force.

147
00:13:18,250 --> 00:13:20,420
-噢，不行 -你会开上人行道
Good, good. No, you're going on the sidewalk.

148
00:13:20,500 --> 00:13:21,510
很好
Okay.

149
00:13:22,880 --> 00:13:24,590
倒车倒车
Back, back, back.

150
00:13:24,680 --> 00:13:25,680
另一边
Go away.

151
00:13:28,140 --> 00:13:29,890
停下来
-Stop. Stop.

152
00:13:36,520 --> 00:13:37,480
可恶
Ah, shit.

153
00:13:37,560 --> 00:13:39,440
他在搞什么鬼？
What the hell is he doing?

154
00:13:39,520 --> 00:13:42,280
没错，我也是这么说
Yes! Exactly! That's exactly what I was saying.

155
00:13:42,360 --> 00:13:45,900
你们不能随便开进来
-Hey, you can't just drive here.

156
00:13:45,990 --> 00:13:47,910
我没开车，我在开车吗？
I'm not driving. Am I driving the car? No.

157
00:13:47,990 --> 00:13:50,240
没有许可证不能开车进来
You can't just bring a car on this street without a permit.

158
00:13:50,330 --> 00:13:53,540
我们有停车许可证，这里，瞧？
No, we have a parking permit. Right here. See?

159
00:13:53,620 --> 00:13:55,660
你放在口袋干嘛？
What the hell's it doing in your pocket?!

160
00:13:55,750 --> 00:13:57,460
我是驾驶啊
Well, I'm the driver.

161
00:13:58,710 --> 00:14:00,840
我们在这里租屋
We're renting here. Yeah.

162
00:14:00,920 --> 00:14:02,000
206号
In 206.

163
00:14:05,970 --> 00:14:07,130
那也不代表 你可以把拖车停在门口
That doesn't mean you can back the trailer up to your front door.

164
00:14:09,260 --> 00:14:12,850
其实我只是想路边停车
No, I wasn't. I was, uh, parallel parking.

165
00:14:12,930 --> 00:14:14,020
哪个路边？
Parallel to what?

166
00:14:16,190 --> 00:14:19,350
我停得不是很好，对吧？
Yeah, that, uh, didn't go so well, huh?

167
00:14:19,440 --> 00:14:21,150
我会再试一次
I'll just give it another try.

168
00:14:21,230 --> 00:14:22,360
我的天啊
-Oh, my God.

169
00:14:25,070 --> 00:14:25,990
好吧
Okay.

170
00:14:30,530 --> 00:14:31,660
很好
Good. Good!

171
00:14:31,740 --> 00:14:34,040
继续倒车
Keep backing away. Keep backing away.

172
00:14:34,120 --> 00:14:35,500
再退后一点
Now go away more.

173
00:14:35,580 --> 00:14:36,790
好了，我行的
Okay, I got this.

174
00:14:38,290 --> 00:14:40,380
-先往另一边 -小心点
The other way, but first the other way.

175
00:14:40,460 --> 00:14:41,670
这就对了
-Easy. -Exactamente.

176
00:14:41,750 --> 00:14:43,710
-小心点 -很好
-Easy, easy. -Uh-huh. Good.

177
00:14:43,800 --> 00:14:45,710
不不不，不对！
No. No, no. What? No!

178
00:14:46,760 --> 00:14:49,510
不不不，停下来！
-No, no, no! Stop! Stop, stop, stop! Stop!

179
00:14:49,590 --> 00:14:51,470
停下来！下车
-Stop! Stop. Get outta the car.

180
00:14:52,140 --> 00:14:53,680
-下车 -对不起
-Get outta the car. -I'm sorry.

181
00:14:53,760 --> 00:14:55,310
你不会倒车
How you could make it this far through life

182
00:14:55,350 --> 00:14:57,390
怎么能活到现在
without knowing how to back up a trailer.

183
00:14:57,480 --> 00:15:01,400
就连只有一只脚的狗狗 都能停得比你好
My God, a dog with one front paw and cataracts coulda done better than that.

184
00:15:01,480 --> 00:15:03,820
而且是自排车，给我钥匙
And an automatic, of course. Give me the keys.

185
00:15:04,480 --> 00:15:06,530
钥匙在瓶架里
Oh, they're in the cupholder.

186
