酷喔，要过来吃午饭吗？
Oh. Cool. You wanna come over for lunch, then?

382
00:31:38,520 --> 00:31:41,270
午饭
-Lunch.

383
00:31:42,110 --> 00:31:42,940
对啊
Yeah.

384
00:31:43,020 --> 00:31:44,610
不，不
No, no.

385
00:31:44,690 --> 00:31:47,570
有兴趣的话今天吃猪里肌肉
Well, it's pork tenderloin, in case you change your mind!

386
00:31:47,650 --> 00:31:49,150
不不不
No, no, no, no.

387
00:31:50,160 --> 00:31:51,370
嘿，不好意思
Hey, excuse me.

388
00:31:53,950 --> 00:31:55,120
就是你
It was you.

389
00:31:55,620 --> 00:31:59,920
这是私人道路，铁门是用来减少车流
This is a private road, and these gates are to keep down the flow of traffic.

390
00:32:00,000 --> 00:32:03,540
不是让白痴驾驶把车开上草地
Not so idiot drivers can go around them and tear up the grass.

391
00:32:03,630 --> 00:32:06,840
被你逮到了，我是建商员工
-Okay. You got me. I'm with Dye & Merika.

392
00:32:06,920 --> 00:32:10,590
我会请管理员来帮你修好
I'm gonna have the groundskeeper come down and fix that up for ya, okay?

393
00:32:10,680 --> 00:32:13,720
比新的更好，祝你愉快
Good as new. Even better. You have a good one now, okay?

394
00:32:13,800 --> 00:32:15,600
规定就是规定
The rules are here for a reason.

395
00:32:20,640 --> 00:32:22,150
我知道你们想干嘛
I know what you guys are up to.

396
00:32:22,230 --> 00:32:24,440
好吧，安德森先生，你说了算
Okay, Mr Anderson. Whatever you say.

397
00:32:25,150 --> 00:32:26,820
继续守望相助
Keep up the neighbourhood watch.

398
00:32:29,320 --> 00:32:33,070
快出来，你这小家伙
-Get out here, you little bugger!

399
00:32:34,120 --> 00:32:35,530
出来啊
Come on. Yeah.

400
00:32:35,620 --> 00:32:36,620
快给我出来！
Get out here!

401
00:32:37,290 --> 00:32:38,750
妳敢再丢一块石头，我就会
You throw one more rock,

402
00:32:38,830 --> 00:32:41,620
把妳的臭狗踢到屋顶
and I swear I'll dropkick that little rat dog of yours right over the roof.

403
00:32:41,710 --> 00:32:45,380
我不是向你家丢石头，那只猫抓伤王子
No, I'm not throwing it at your house. That nasty cat scratched Prince.

404
00:32:45,460 --> 00:32:46,630
我要杀了那只臭猫
I'm gonna kill that piece of shit.

405
00:32:46,710 --> 00:32:47,840
想都别想
No, you're not.

406
00:32:47,920 --> 00:32:49,670
关你什么事？那是只野猫
What do you care? It's feral.

407
00:32:49,760 --> 00:32:52,220
全身上下可能都是病
It's probably full of all sorts of disgusting diseases.

408
00:32:52,300 --> 00:32:54,680
妳也一样，但我不会向妳丢石头
So are you, most likely. I don't throw rocks at you.

409
00:32:55,760 --> 00:32:56,600
安迪
Andy.

410
00:32:56,680 --> 00:32:57,510
怎么了？
-What's up? -Did you hear what he just said this time?

411
00:32:57,600 --> 00:32:59,520
你听到他这次骂我什么吗？

412
00:32:59,600 --> 00:33:01,350
我跟你说过他常骂我
I told you before about how he talks to me.

413
00:33:01,440 --> 00:33:03,520
赶快逃吧
Get outta here while you can.

414
00:33:03,600 --> 00:33:04,810
我不是你的朋友
I'm not your friend.

415
00:33:04,900 --> 00:33:07,570
建商说要把老人家都送到安养院
Dye & Merika said they'll get all the old people on this street into a home.

416
00:33:07,650 --> 00:33:08,980
越快越好！
The sooner the better!

417
00:33:26,960 --> 00:33:29,300
你好 又怎么了？
-Hello. -What now?

418
00:33:29,460 --> 00:33:31,590
我只想把扳手还给你
I just wanted to bring the wrenches back.

419
00:33:31,670 --> 00:33:34,510
我找到家具附上的扳手 恭喜了
-I found one that came with the furniture. -Congratulations.

420
00:33:35,220 --> 00:33:37,470
我为你做了沙波洛
And I made you some salpores de arroz.

421
00:33:37,550 --> 00:33:39,390
巧克力酱炖鸡？
Is that chicken and mole?

422
00:33:39,470 --> 00:33:43,940
不是，这是萨尔瓦多饼干，我爸的最爱
No. These are Salvadoran cookies. They were my father's favourite, so...

423
00:33:44,020 --> 00:33:45,810
很好吃喔，你一定会超爱
They're delicious. You're gonna love 'em.

424
00:33:45,900 --> 00:33:47,270
对啊，因为是我做的
Yes, because I made them.

425
00:33:47,360 --> 00:33:50,530
另外我也想向你借梯子
Also, Otto, I was wondering if you have a ladder I can borrow.

426
00:33:50,610 --> 00:33:51,940
我们的窗户卡住了
Our window is jammed.

427
00:33:52,030 --> 00:33:53,570
你为什么需要梯子？
Why do you need a ladder?

428
00:33:53,650 --> 00:33:55,820
是上面的窗户
Well, it's the one up there.

429
00:33:57,070 --> 00:33:58,370
打不开
It won't open.

430
00:33:58,450 --> 00:34:00,950
你想试着从外面打开？
And you're gonna try to open it from the outside?

431
00:34:01,040 --> 00:34:02,290
对，没错
Yeah. Right.

432
00:34:03,710 --> 00:34:05,040
我去穿大衣
I'll get my coat.

433
00:34:05,120 --> 00:34:06,540
好，谢谢你
Okay. Thank you.

434
00:34:08,840 --> 00:34:10,340
我喜欢他挥手的样子
I like how his hands are waving.

435
00:34:10,420 --> 00:34:12,130
把手插上去
Let's put the arm in.

436
00:34:14,670 --> 00:34:15,550
-太好了 -安妮塔
-Good. -Anita.

437
00:34:15,630 --> 00:34:20,180
奥托，打扰一下，我们的暖气坏了
Uh, Otto, hate to bother you, but, um, we don't have any heat.

438
00:34:21,010 --> 00:34:22,720
能不能来看看？
Could you come take a look?

439
00:34:22,810 --> 00:34:24,230
试试替散热器排水
Try bleeding your radiators.

440
00:34:25,230 --> 00:34:27,650
我该怎么做？
How would I go about that?

441
00:34:27,730 --> 00:34:30,020
替散热器排水
By bleeding the radiators.

442
00:34:30,110 --> 00:34:32,030
奥托，别这么难搞
Otto. Don't be rude.

443
00:34:32,110 --> 00:34:33,730
我没有难搞
I wasn't being rude.

444
00:34:34,440 --> 00:34:38,320
有时候很难看得出来
Well, it's hard to tell the difference sometimes with Otto.

445
00:34:38,410 --> 00:34:39,410
是啊
Yeah.

446
00:34:40,370 --> 00:34:43,660
对了，我们才刚搬进206号
By the way, we, uh, just moved to 206.

447
00:34:44,250 --> 00:34:45,960
-我是玛丽索 -我是汤米
-I'm Marisol. -I'm Tommy.

448
00:34:46,040 --> 00:34:48,130
-欢迎 -幸会了
-Welcome, honey. -Nice meeting you.

449
00:34:48,210 --> 00:34:49,290
我是安妮塔
I'm Anita.

450
00:34:49,380 --> 00:34:52,340
我老公鲁本以前负责处理暖气
My husband, Reuben, is the one who used to handle the heat.

451
00:34:52,420 --> 00:34:54,670
但我们知道总有一天
-Okay. -But we always knew a day would come

452
00:34:54,760 --> 00:34:58,550
他会没办法处理这些事情
when he wouldn't be able to handle things around the house any longer.

453
00:34:59,800 --> 00:35:03,310
鲁本把我踢出管委会时应该先想到
Maybe Reuben should have thought of that when he organised his coup.

454
00:35:04,430 --> 00:35:07,020
那是很久以前的事
That was a long time ago.

455
00:35:07,100 --> 00:35:08,270
踢出管委会？
A coup?

456
00:35:08,350 --> 00:35:10,360
那是个误会
It was a misunderstanding.

457
00:35:10,440 --> 00:35:11,520
他把我踢出去
It was a coup.

458
00:35:14,150 --> 00:35:18,660
奥托，快去帮安妮塔替散热器排气
Otto, can't you just go breathe Anita's radiators for her?

459
00:35:18,740 --> 00:35:21,530
不，不能替散热器排气
No. Because you don't breathe radiators.

460
00:35:21,620 --> 00:35:22,660
要替散热器排水
You bleed them.

461
00:35:22,740 --> 00:35:24,750
-看看这块坡道 -那是索妮娅的
-Honey, look at this ramp. -That's Sonya's.

462
00:35:24,830 --> 00:35:26,910
-拉拖车时就需要 -放下来
-This is what we needed for the trailer. -Put that down.

463
00:35:27,500 --> 00:35:29,830
放下来！谁说你能碰它？
Put that down! Who said you could touch that?!

464
00:35:29,920 --> 00:35:32,170
-对不起 -你们全都给我滚
-Sorry. -All of you get outta here. Go, go.

465
00:35:32,250 --> 00:35:35,090
拿了梯子就滚，全都给我滚
Take your ladder and go. Get outta here. All of you.

466
00:35:35,170 --> 00:35:36,550
-好啦 -谢谢你
-Okay. -Thank you.

467
00:35:37,880 --> 00:35:38,930
-谢谢你 -小心
Watch out.

468
00:35:39,010 --> 00:35:41,680
好了
-Right. Right.

469
00:35:45,430 --> 00:35:46,810
-谢谢你
-Thank you! -Thank you!

470
00:35:52,480 --> 00:35:55,150
不行，你在这里干嘛？
No. What are you doing in here?

471
00:35:55,230 --> 00:35:57,110
你怎么会躲到里面？
How did you get in here? Come on.

472
00:35:57,190 --> 00:35:59,610
快滚！给我出去
Come on. Go! Get outta there.

473
00:36:01,200 --> 00:36:03,740
出去，出去
No, get out. Get out of there.

474
00:36:03,830 --> 00:36:04,830
快滚啊
Come on, go.

475
00:36:07,790 --> 00:36:08,620
嘿
-Hey.

476
00:36:12,130 --> 00:36:13,500
放开！
Let go!

477
00:36:14,250 --> 00:36:15,380
放开
-Let go.

478
00:36:18,760 --> 00:36:21,550
你敢抓伤我，我就咬你
You scratch me, I'll bite you.

479
00:36:24,850 --> 00:36:26,060
学会教训了吧
-That'll teach you.

480
00:36:30,390 --> 00:36:31,600
蠢猫
Stupid cat.

481
00:36:36,610 --> 00:36:38,690
-嗨，奥托
-Hi, Otto!

482
00:36:38,780 --> 00:36:40,450
-O-T-T-O.
O-T-T-O

483
00:36:58,300 --> 00:36:59,300
奥托
Otto. Um...

484
00:37:00,300 --> 00:37:01,880
我去年八月借水管给妳
I loaned you my garden hose last August.

485
00:37:01,970 --> 00:37:05,050
只要还给我，我就帮妳替暖气排水
If you give it back to me, I'll bleed your radiators for you.

486
00:37:06,810 --> 00:37:07,850
进来吧
Come in.

487
00:37:15,310 --> 00:37:19,990
你的新邻居看起来人很好，对吧？
So those new neighbours of yours, they seem quite lovely, don't you think?

488
00:37:20,860 --> 00:37:21,860
好到不行
Lovely.

489
00:37:22,570 --> 00:37:26,620
你可能很快就会有更多邻居了
Yeah, well, you may have some more new neighbours soon enough.

490
00:37:27,740 --> 00:37:30,120
建商的人告诉我们…
The realty people, they've been telling us...

491
00:37:30,950 --> 00:37:33,460
我和鲁本必须搬走
Reuben and I have to move out.

492
00:37:34,250 --> 00:37:35,500
那全是屁话
No, that's a load of crap.

493
00:37:36,630 --> 00:37:38,300
这房子是你们的
They don't own this house. You do.

494
00:37:38,380 --> 00:37:40,050
我也是这么说
Yeah, well, that's what I said.

495
00:37:40,760 --> 00:37:43,590
他们找上我们的儿子克里斯
They, uh, have been talking to our boy, Chris.

496
00:37:44,550 --> 00:37:47,800
他说我照顾不了鲁本
Now he's saying that I can no longer take care of Reuben,

497
00:37:47,890 --> 00:37:51,020
必须把他送去护理之家
that he needs to be in a special care place.

498
00:37:51,100 --> 00:37:54,850
我也应该搬去安养院
And I should move into a retirement home.

499
00:37:54,940 --> 00:37:57,980
克里斯懂什么？他是个白痴
What does Chris know about it? He's an idiot. He always has been.

500
00:37:58,070 --> 00:37:59,980
他们不能逼妳做任何事
They can't make you do anything.

501
00:38:03,360 --> 00:38:05,070
他知道我们在这里吗？
Does he even know we're here?

502
00:38:05,820 --> 00:38:07,070
当然知道
Of course he does.

503
00:38:07,160 --> 00:38:08,950
别被他骗了
Don't let him fool you.

504
00:38:09,870 --> 00:38:11,080
他头脑很清楚
He's still in there.

505
00:38:15,000 --> 00:38:17,000
我去拿你的水管
Let me go find your hose.

506
00:38:35,810 --> 00:38:38,400
这整个社区就快完蛋了
The whole neighbourhood is falling apart these days.

507
00:38:39,900 --> 00:38:42,650
就连管委会都没有了
They don't even have a homeowners' association anymore.

508
00:38:44,030 --> 00:38:47,160
没有人管理社区的事
No one left to keep things running.

509
00:38:48,990 --> 00:38:50,370
不像我们以前那样
Not like we did.

510
00:38:57,420 --> 00:38:58,880
我得把话说清楚
Now, just to be clear...

511
00:39:00,130 --> 00:39:01,670
我还没原谅你
I still haven't forgiven you.

512
00:39:03,170 --> 00:39:06,430
我只是没想到你病得这么快
I just didn't realise you would fall to shit so quickly.

513
00:39:07,680 --> 00:39:08,720
现在…
Now...

514
00:39:10,550 --> 00:39:13,520
他们要毁了我们努力建立的家园
they're tearing apart everything we worked so hard to build.

515
00:39:15,140 --> 00:39:17,900
我都还没走，他们就想把我们赶走
I haven't even left yet, and they're trying to erase us.

516
00:39:20,110 --> 00:39:24,360
我不会留下来看到那种事发生
Well, I am not staying around to see that happen.

517
00:39:25,280 --> 00:39:26,530
我要走了
I'm leaving.

518
00:39:27,990 --> 00:39:29,030
永远离开
-For good. -You ready for lunch?

519
00:39:29,110 --> 00:39:30,280
午饭准备好了吗？

520
00:39:30,370 --> 00:39:32,120
-我做了你爱吃的奶油玉米
I'm making that creamed corn you like.

521
00:39:32,200 --> 00:39:33,200
-谢谢妳
Oh, thank you.

522
00:39:33,990 --> 00:39:36,960
谢谢你，奥托，抱歉拖了这么久
Thank you, Otto. I'm sorry it took so long to give it back.

523
00:39:37,040 --> 00:39:38,420
一起吃午饭？
Um, you wanna stay for lunch?

524
00:39:38,500 --> 00:39:40,290
安妮塔做了猪里肌肉
Yeah, Anita made a pork tenderloin.

525
00:39:40,380 --> 00:39:42,540
不了，我有很多事要做
No, I have a lot of things I have to do.

526
00:39:45,880 --> 00:39:47,170
鲁本，你在干嘛？
Reuben, what are you doing, hon?

527
00:39:49,090 --> 00:39:50,340
-放手 -你在干嘛？
-Let go. -What are you doing?

528
00:39:51,180 --> 00:39:54,350
-放手 -鲁本
-Let go. -Reuben. Reuben.

529
00:39:54,430 --> 00:39:56,430
放…你在干嘛？
-Let... -What are you doing?

530
00:39:56,520 --> 00:39:57,350
…手
...go.

531
00:40:09,150 --> 00:40:10,160
天啊
Oh, man.

532
00:40:31,840 --> 00:40:33,760
试试从里头打开
Try opening it from the inside a little.

533
00:40:36,060 --> 00:40:37,560
比我想像的更高
It's higher than I thought.

534
00:40:38,600 --> 00:40:40,230
我有点头晕
I'm a little bit dizzy, honey.

