00:42:31,760 --> 00:42:35,180
♪ That there's no colour ♪

548
00:42:35,260 --> 00:42:37,640
♪ In the world without you ♪

549
00:42:43,640 --> 00:42:46,690
看来我们都得搭下一班火车
Looks like we'll both have to take the next one.

550
00:42:49,270 --> 00:42:50,110
奥托
Otto.

551
00:42:50,190 --> 00:42:52,110
那是你爸的名字
It was your father's name.

552
00:42:52,190 --> 00:42:53,280
妳还记得
You remembered.

553
00:42:56,570 --> 00:42:58,910
你得回去军营吗？
Did you have to go back to the military centre?

554
00:42:58,990 --> 00:43:01,790
不，我想把车票钱还给妳
No, I wanted to pay you back for the train ticket.

555
00:43:04,290 --> 00:43:06,420
请我吃晚饭不是更好吗？
Wouldn't it be nicer if you invited me to dinner?

556
00:43:08,130 --> 00:43:10,750
♪ The best gift of this life ♪

557
00:43:12,130 --> 00:43:15,010
♪ Is to see you up close ♪

558
00:43:16,380 --> 00:43:17,680
♪ And now and again... ♪

559
00:43:17,760 --> 00:43:18,930
要进去吗？
Shall we?

560
00:43:19,010 --> 00:43:20,220
好啊，进去吧
Yeah, let's go in.

