00:43:40,320 --> 00:43:41,490
怎么说？
Interest me like...?

569
00:43:41,580 --> 00:43:42,950
你对什么有热情？
What are you passionate about?

570
00:43:43,910 --> 00:43:46,000
机器，引擎
Machines. Engines.

571
00:43:46,080 --> 00:43:47,500
我想知道东西怎么运作
I like knowing how things work.

