不重要，我得借用妳的手机
I just need to use your phone, okay?

1411
01:37:33,890 --> 01:37:35,060
你知道吗？
You know what?

1412
01:37:35,140 --> 01:37:36,140
不行
No.

1413
01:37:36,230 --> 01:37:37,690
-不行？ -不行
-No? -No.

1414
01:37:38,810 --> 01:37:41,520
你不肯说你的手机为何停话
You won't tell me why your phone is disconnected?

1415
01:37:41,610 --> 01:37:44,940
也不肯说为何要借用我的手机
You won't tell me why you need to use my phone?

1416
01:37:45,030 --> 01:37:48,030
更不肯说你昨天在街上怎么了
You won't tell me what happened to you in the street yesterday?

1417
01:37:48,820 --> 01:37:51,950
然后回家连门都不肯打开
And then you went inside and you wouldn't even open the door?

1418
01:37:53,870 --> 01:37:55,450
你把我吓坏了，奥托
You scared me, Otto.

1419
01:37:57,210 --> 01:37:59,250
你知道我在门外等了多久吗？
Do you know how long I was out there?

1420
01:37:59,330 --> 01:38:02,290
我不知道你是不是出了事
And I didn't know if something had happened to you.

1421
01:38:03,710 --> 01:38:05,800
或是你会出什么事
Or if something was gonna happen to you.

1422
01:38:07,090 --> 01:38:10,550
很抱歉我提到索妮娅的大衣
And I'm sorry if I said the wrong thing about Sonya's coats.

1423
01:38:10,640 --> 01:38:12,050
但我只是想帮忙
But I was just trying to help.

1424
01:38:13,470 --> 01:38:16,390
你却把我拒之门外
And you left me out there.

1425
01:38:18,390 --> 01:38:21,190
所以你不能借用我的手机
So, no. You can't use my phone.

1426
01:38:27,240 --> 01:38:30,570
