You think your life is so hard because everybody's an idiot

1427
01:38:30,660 --> 01:38:32,450
你得自己扛下所有事，对吗？
and you have to do everything on your own, right?

1428
01:38:34,160 --> 01:38:34,990
对吗？
Right?

1429
01:38:36,330 --> 01:38:37,330
猜怎么着？
But guess what.

1430
01:38:38,460 --> 01:38:39,670
你办不到
You can't.

1431
01:38:40,920 --> 01:38:41,920
没人办得到
No one can.

1432
01:38:43,340 --> 01:38:44,960
你应该感到高兴
And I think you should just be happy

1433
01:38:45,050 --> 01:38:47,380
有人想帮你度过糟糕的一天
that someone was trying to help you get through a crappy day.

1434
01:38:49,050 --> 01:38:50,550
就算他们是白痴
Even if they're an idiot.

1435
01:38:51,720 --> 01:38:54,050
所以…建商那些混蛋
-So... -The real estate bastards

1436
01:38:54,140 --> 01:38:57,100
想把安妮塔和鲁本赶出他们家
are trying to force Anita and Reuben out of their home.

1437
01:38:57,850 --> 01:38:59,390
所以我才得借用妳的手机
That's why I need to use your phone.

1438
01:39:03,190 --> 01:39:04,940
好吧，进来吧
Okay, fine. Come on.

1439
01:39:21,460 --> 01:39:23,330
我们从来没度过假
We had never had a vacation.

1440
01:39:27,710 --> 01:39:29,260
索妮娅怀胎六个月
Sonya was six months pregnant.

1441
01:39:30,550 --> 01:39:34,220
她想趁宝宝出生前做点特别的
And she wanted to do something special before the baby came.

1442
01:39:35,010 --> 01:39:37,510
于是我们就决定去尼加拉大瀑布
So we booked a trip to Niagara Falls.

1443
01:39:39,560 --> 01:39:41,440
回程时客运出车祸
On the way back, the bus crashed.

1444
01:39:43,100 --> 01:39:45,690
车厂召回刹车线
There'd been a recall on the brake lines,

1445
01:39:45,770 --> 01:39:47,820
但客运公司从没修好
but the company never had them fixed.

1446
01:39:49,480 --> 01:39:50,860
索妮娅半身瘫痪，而且…
Sonya was paralyzed...

1447
01:39:52,450 --> 01:39:54,450
我们也失去了儿子
and we lost our son.

1448
01:39:58,370 --> 01:40:00,790
三个月后她终于能回家
After three months, she was finally able to come home.

1449
01:40:01,870 --> 01:40:04,790
但他们已经开始盖新公寓
But they had started building the new condos

1450
01:40:04,880 --> 01:40:08,090
还有社区中心和步道
and the community centre and the walkways,

1451
01:40:08,170 --> 01:40:11,300
全都不是无障碍空间
none of which were designed for people in wheelchairs.

1452
01:40:12,170 --> 01:40:14,800
建商大可以修改设计蓝图
The builders could have changed their plans.

1453
01:40:15,680 --> 01:40:20,060
