But the laws weren't in place back then, and they didn't care.

1454
01:40:20,680 --> 01:40:21,770
我在乎
I did.

1455
01:40:21,850 --> 01:40:25,230
我非常在乎
-We're putting in a new playground... -I cared.

1456
01:40:25,310 --> 01:40:28,070
-你太太这种人… -我好生气
-There's places for people like your wife. -And I was so angry.

1457
01:40:28,150 --> 01:40:31,240
什么意思？她这种人？什么意思？
What does that mean? People like her? What does that mean?

1458
01:40:31,320 --> 01:40:33,780
-你想说什么？ -放开我！
-What're you tryin' to say?! -Get off of me!

1459
01:40:34,490 --> 01:40:38,830
于是他们就把我踢出管委会
That's when they voted me out as head of the homeowners' association.

1460
01:40:41,040 --> 01:40:43,080
我想彻底毁掉他们
I wanted to obliterate them all.

1461
01:40:43,160 --> 01:40:46,920
建商、房地商、客运公司和司机
The builders, and the realtors, and the bus company, the bus driver.

1462
01:40:47,000 --> 01:40:48,630
我本来永远无法放手…
I never would have let it go...

1463
01:40:50,340 --> 01:40:51,340
要是没有索妮娅
but for Sonya.

1464
01:40:52,880 --> 01:40:54,550
索妮娅说我们必须继续过活
Sonya said we had to keep living.

1465
01:40:57,800 --> 01:40:58,890
我就那么做
That's what I did.

1466
01:41:00,510 --> 01:41:01,770
我为了索妮娅继续过活
I lived for Sonya.

1467
01:41:06,350 --> 01:41:08,020
她半年前去世
Six months ago she passed away.

1468
01:41:08,900 --> 01:41:09,900
癌症
Cancer.

1469
01:41:14,150 --> 01:41:15,450
我本来也想寻死
I was going to join her.

1470
01:41:17,280 --> 01:41:19,660
所以才会停用手机
That's why I had them disconnect my phone.

1471
01:41:22,700 --> 01:41:25,790
但现在我觉得她要我继续过活
But now I think she wants me to keep living.

1472
01:41:28,420 --> 01:41:31,170
我也有事要做
And I have things to do.

1473
01:41:35,340 --> 01:41:38,140
"雪莉肯锡"

1474
01:42:03,160 --> 01:42:04,870
你在浪费时间，奥托
You're wasting your time, Otto.

1475
01:42:04,950 --> 01:42:07,410
木已成舟，鲁本要跟我们走
It's a done deal. Reuben's coming with us.

1476
01:42:07,500 --> 01:42:09,540
你敢挡路
And if you get in our way,

1477
01:42:09,630 --> 01:42:10,880
我就请警察逮捕你
I'll have you arrested.

1478
01:42:11,500 --> 01:42:12,420
我什么都没做 别再向前走一步
-I'm not doing a thing. -Don't you take another step.

1479
01:42:15,300 --> 01:42:17,050
你不能把我先生带走
You are not taking my husband away from me.

1480
01:42:17,800 --> 01:42:21,300
安妮塔，我们这是为妳好
Anita, please. We're doing this for your own good.

1481
01:42:21,390 --> 01:42:24,470
你想抢走我的房子
What you're doing is trying to take my property.

1482
01:42:25,350 --> 01:42:26,600
我要鲁本 留下来跟我一起…
I want Reuben to stay right here for the rest of his life,

1483
01:42:28,190 --> 01:42:29,600
"长照部门"

1484
01:42:29,690 --> 01:42:31,610
…在家度过余生
with me in our home.

1485
