妳不行了，谁会照顾鲁本？
Okay, but who's gonna take care of Reuben when you're no longer able to?

1486
01:42:35,940 --> 01:42:38,360
谁会照顾妳？奥托？
Who's gonna take care of you? Otto?

1487
01:42:38,450 --> 01:42:41,450
奥托的身体也不行了，对吧？
Otto's not in the best health either. Are you, Otto?

1488
01:42:42,570 --> 01:42:43,780
我会照顾他们
I'll take care of 'em.

1489
01:42:45,080 --> 01:42:48,580
你在干嘛？放下来 安妮塔和鲁本就像我的家人
-What are you doing? Put that down. -Anita and Reuben are like family to me.

1490
01:42:48,660 --> 01:42:50,420
只要他们需要，我就会照顾他们
I'll take care of them as long as they need.

1491
01:42:50,960 --> 01:42:52,580
他们不是你家人
They're not your family.

1492
01:42:52,670 --> 01:42:56,210
他们的儿子克里斯决定他们无法自理
Uh, their son, Chris, has decided they're not fit enough to be on their own,

1493
01:42:56,300 --> 01:42:58,220
所以我们只是…
and so what we're doing is--

1494
01:42:58,300 --> 01:42:59,380
不好意思
Excuse me. When was the last time Chris saw his parents?

1495
01:42:59,510 --> 01:43:01,640
克里斯上次见他父母是何时？

1496
01:43:01,720 --> 01:43:05,390
他住在日本，十年没跟父母联络
He lives in Japan. They've been estranged for 10 years.

1497
01:43:05,470 --> 01:43:07,770
克里斯不清楚他父母的状况
Chris would have no idea how his parents are doing,

1498
01:43:07,850 --> 01:43:09,520
除了你跟他说的
except for what you told him.

1499
01:43:09,600 --> 01:43:11,440
妳又是谁？
Okay. And who are you?

1500
01:43:11,520 --> 01:43:13,400
我是雪莉肯锡
My name is Shari Kenzie.

1501
01:43:13,480 --> 01:43:15,400
社群媒体记者
Social media journalist.

1502
01:43:15,480 --> 01:43:17,650
我们现在正在直播
-We're streaming live right now. -Uh...

1503
01:43:18,360 --> 01:43:21,780
够了…关掉摄影机，不准乱拍
All right, all right, shut that camera off. You can't film this.

1504
01:43:21,860 --> 01:43:23,660
人行道是公共区域
It's a public sidewalk.

1505
01:43:24,320 --> 01:43:26,990
你跟安妮塔儿子说她得了帕金森，但…
You told Anita's son, Chris, that she had Parkinson's,

1506
01:43:27,080 --> 01:43:30,870
她从来没说过她的诊断结果
but Anita never told anyone about her diagnosis.

1507
01:43:30,960 --> 01:43:33,040
你怎么会知道？
So how did you know?

1508
01:43:33,130 --> 01:43:35,250
我得查一下记录
I'd have to check the records.

1509
01:43:36,130 --> 01:43:38,960
安德森先生算是本地英雄
Mr Anderson over there is something of a local hero.

1510
01:43:39,050 --> 01:43:41,430
他说你也知道
He tells me you know details about his private health records as well.

1511
01:43:41,680 --> 01:43:44,260
他的私人就诊资料

